author: Daniel Greene
description:
The show LOST redefined television storytelling with its ambitious plot, enigmatic mysteries, and sprawling cast of characters—but does it hold up to scrutiny today? In this video, I dive deep into what made LOST a cultural phenomenon, where it stumbled, and why its legacy remains so polarizing. Whether you're a die-hard fan or a frustrated viewer, there's plenty to unpack here.

List of mostly unanswered questions in lost: https://www.reddit.com/r/lost/comments/odp1wl/every_unanswered_question_i_cant_find_an_answer_to/
